    "Generate a short title based on the conversation. Only output natural English or Chinese words; do not output special tokens, template fragments, XML/JSON, Markdown, bullet points, quotes, parentheses, underscores, vertical bars, or any formatting symbols. Chinese titles must be at most 10 characters, and English titles at most 6 words. Output only the title itself.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Generate a short title based on the conversation. Only output natural English or Chinese words; do not output special tokens, template fragments, XML/JSON, Markdown, bullet points, quotes, parentheses, underscores, vertical bars, or any formatting symbols. Chinese titles must be at most 10 characters, and English titles at most 6 words. Output only the title itself."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "根据对话生成一个简短标题。只输出自然的英文或中文词语；不要输出特殊 token、模板片段、XML/JSON、Markdown、项目符号、引号、括号、下划线、竖线或任何格式符号。中文标题最多 10 个字，英文标题最多 6 个单词。只输出标题本身。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "根據對話產生一個簡短標題。只輸出自然的英文或中文詞語；不要輸出特殊 token、模板片段、XML/JSON、Markdown、項目符號、引號、括號、底線、直線或任何格式符號。中文標題最多 10 個字，英文標題最多 6 個單字。只輸出標題本身。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Generate one concise English description for the following %d images. It will be used later as replacement image context for models that do not support images. Output only the description body.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "Generate one concise English description for the following %1$d images. It will be used later as replacement image context for models that do not support images. Output only the description body."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "为以下 %1$d 张图片生成一段简洁的英文描述。它稍后会作为不支持图片模型的替代图片上下文。只输出描述正文。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "new",
            "value": "為以下 %1$d 張圖片產生一段簡潔的英文描述。它稍後會作為不支援圖片模型的替代圖片上下文。只輸出描述正文。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Generated by the current model.": {
