    },
    "Skills 只作为上下文指令注入模型，不会在 iPhone 上执行脚本、Python 或本地命令。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Skills are only injected into the model as context instructions. They do not run scripts, Python, or local commands on iPhone."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Skills 只作为上下文指令注入模型，不会在 iPhone 上执行脚本、Python 或本地命令。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Skills 只作為上下文指令注入模型，不會在 iPhone 上執行指令碼、Python 或本機命令。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Skills 是文本指令包；MCP 仅支持远程 HTTPS 服务器。本机不会执行 Python、shell 或本地脚本。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Skills are text instruction packages. MCP only supports remote HTTPS servers. This device will not run Python, shell commands, or local scripts."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Skills 是文本指令包；MCP 仅支持远程 HTTPS 服务器。本机不会执行 Python、shell 或本地脚本。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Skills 是文字指令包；MCP 僅支援遠端 HTTPS 伺服器。本機不會執行 Python、shell 或本機指令碼。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
