    "仅支持远程 HTTPS MCP。默认需要逐次确认；关闭确认后，模型可在启用该 MCP 时自动发起远程调用。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Only remote HTTPS MCP servers are supported. Each call requires approval by default; when confirmation is disabled, the model can make remote calls automatically while the MCP is enabled."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "仅支持远程 HTTPS MCP。默认需要逐次确认；关闭确认后，模型可在启用该 MCP 时自动发起远程调用。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "僅支援遠端 HTTPS MCP。預設每次呼叫都需要確認；關閉確認後，模型可在啟用該 MCP 時自動進行遠端呼叫。"
          }
        }
