    "提示词预设会在所有配置中共享。当前选中的内容会作为每次对话的 system message 发送。留空则不发送提示词。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Prompt presets are shared across all configurations. The selected content is sent as the system message for each conversation. Leave it blank to send no prompt."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "提示词预设会在所有配置中共享。当前选中的内容会作为每次对话的 system message 发送。留空则不发送提示词。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
